  <bioghist id="46557fe05da4351a9bd0ba311275f421">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Ruth Mayleas was Director of Theatre Program at the National Education Association from 1966-78. In 1982, she joined the Ford Foundation as a program officer, later advisor, in the Education and Culture department. While at Ford, she supported performing arts, including theatre and visual arts, with a focus on minority arts organizations. Mayleas left the Foundation in 1994.</p>  </bioghist>
